Usage: undo_uniquify_partition [-help]
                               -hinst <master hierarchical_instance_name>
                               [-preserve_routes]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-hinst <master hierarchical_instance_name>
                     # Specifies name of the hierarchical instance to uniquify. (string, required)
-preserve_routes     # Preserve routes during undo_uniquify_partition
                     # (bool, optional)